{"tid":2340580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"名人頻掟貨 傳趙國雄逾億賣雅賓利  郭鶴年家族8,500萬沽怡園","createTime":"2020-12-25T15:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T15:22:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b21a5a7557fa1cc3ff00d72879b95f25f031fa6","tid":2340580,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201225/O47HZQ3JUZCXFMDVYJXAK3XVS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201225%2FO47HZQ3JUZCXFMDVYJXAK3XVS4%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=173e2705\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201225%2FO47HZQ3JUZCXFMDVYJXAK3XVS4%2F&h=94a84407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201225/O47HZQ3JUZCXFMDVYJXAK3XVS4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n名人頻掟貨 傳趙國雄逾億賣雅賓利 <br />\n郭鶴年家族8,500萬沽怡園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YWsxRI_urbQWNh08oNDj8KJX3dg=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FWD7TCRW6JHJDOYPWCMABNB4ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYWsxRI_urbQWNh08oNDj8KJX3dg%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFWD7TCRW6JHJDOYPWCMABNB4ZQ.jpg&h=2c77a04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■郭鶴年家族沽出東半山老牌豪宅怡園（箭嘴示），獲利8,235萬元。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】山頂文輝道豪宅地王以刷新紀錄賣出，有「糖王」之稱的郭鶴年家族成員，新近亦以8,500萬元沽出東半山老牌豪宅怡園，打破該豪宅一年來未聞成交悶局；郭氏家族持有豪宅37年，賬面賺逾8,200萬元。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：二手樓價按周再跌0.4%<br />\n<br />\n樓齡55年的黃泥涌峽道怡園2D號中層4室，實用面積2,547方呎，獲買家以8,500萬元承接，呎價3.33萬元。土地註冊處資料，原業主Robenex Investments Limited，公司董事包括郭孔丞（Kuok Khoon Chen）、郭綺光（Kuok Ruth）、張錦綸（Teo Ching Leun）；郭孔丞及郭綺光分別為郭鶴年長子及女兒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n龐維新5,397萬沽上環商厦<br />\n<br />\n家族成員1983年透過公司名義以265萬元買入上址，持貨37年，是次沽出賬面賺8,235萬元，升價31倍，新買家登記為李康蘭。除上述單位，郭綺光亦愛投資豪宅物業，其中今年10月，郭綺光等相關人士以1,370萬元沽Soho 38高層，持貨12年微賺約25萬元；另以2,500萬元沽縉城峰單位。<br />\n<br />\n政府上月底起撤銷雙倍印花稅，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c6t-iMaEuRAAJiU1AQaDDoLv4o4=/1276x1052/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7APENTEVIRHELIAQ4RBH4N2FRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc6t-iMaEuRAAJiU1AQaDDoLv4o4%3D%2F1276x1052%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7APENTEVIRHELIAQ4RBH4N2FRA.gif&h=1714572f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅守輝妻賣葵涌工廈<br />\n<br />\n此外，裕泰興家族成員羅守輝妻子或相關人士，繼早前以2,500萬元沽出鴨脷洲南灣5座中層單位，持貨七年賬面賺220萬元後，新近再沽葵涌工廈。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料，葵昌路美和工業大廈7至9樓全層，總面積19,314方呎，上月26日、即撤銷「雙辣稅」首日，合共以8,790萬元易手，呎價約4,551元。其中7樓由安卓企業有限。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，長實地產執。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a85a4cdede93548380b668853986fdf36b3729c8","tid":2340580,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"惡意拋售資產<br />\n擾亂市場價格<br />\n觸犯國安法"},{"pid":"d6e810a58d368f416a7c0afff7094c609d7bcf03","tid":2340580,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}